OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA brighter day on Wednesday
OL,6,Fcompared to Tuesday with a mix of
OL,7,Fcloud and sunny spells. The odd shower
OL,8,Fpossible but largely dry. Breezy with
OL,9,Ftemperatures near normal.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with clear
OL,12,Fspells initially. Turning cloudier
OL,13,Fovernight along with strengthening
OL,14,Fwinds and some outbreaks of rain. Mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain, locally heavy and persistent at
OL,18,Ftimes. Windy especially over the hills
OL,19,Fand coasts with gales possible.
OL,20,FTurning colder overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
