OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,6,Fwith blustery showers on Friday,
OL,7,Fwintry over the hills. A frosty start
OL,8,Fto Saturday, then largely dry.
OL,9,FBecoming cloudier through Sunday with
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
